%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22'This%20looks%20and%20feels%20like%20the%20year%202000%20to%20me'%3A%20Investing%20legend%20Rob%20Arnott%20says%20the%20stock%20market's%20record%20rally%20reminds%20him%20of%20the%20dot-com%20bubble%20peak%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rob%20Arnott%20Top%20100%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5cafa4e6c57fa62c1321efb8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETim%20Boyle%2FBloomberg%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERob%20Arnott%20warns%20of%20a%20potential%20bear%20market%20in%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20comparisons%20to%20the%20dot-com%20peak%20in%202000%20are%20fair.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20high%20valuations%2C%20driven%20by%20AI%20optimism%2C%20mirror%20past%20market%20peaks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-to-invest-inflation-recession-stock-market-trades-rob-arnott-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERob%20Arnott%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20he's%20usually%20early%20when%20calling%20a%20bull%20market%20top.%20So%20when%20he%20says%20the%20current%20market%20environment%20reminds%20him%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20dot-com%20bubble%20peak%2C%20it%20doesn't%20mean%20he%20thinks%20a%20significant%20pullback%20is%20imminent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20does%20mean%2C%20however%2C%20that%20he%20sees%20a%20big%20decline%20somewhere%20not%20too%20far%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20looks%20and%20feels%20like%20the%20year%202000%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Arnott%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20November%2011.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BAre%20we%20likely%20to%20see%20a%20bear%20market%20in%20the%20next%20two%20years%20for%20large-cap%20growth%3F%20Yeah.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArnott's%20comments%20came%20as%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20%E2%80%94%20a%20large-cap%20index%20dominated%20by%20mega-cap%20growth%20firms%20known%20as%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%20%E2%80%94%20jumped%205%25%20within%20a%20week%20following%20the%20election%20of%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20closing%20above%206%2C000%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20The%20explosive%20move%20was%20the%20latest%20advance%20in%20a%20torrid%2066%25%20rally%20that's%20lasted%20more%20than%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20robust%20economy%20and%20excitement%20about%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20business-friendly%20policies%20from%20the%20future%20Trump%20administration%20have%20propelled%20the%20market%20to%20all-time%20highs.%20But%20Arnott%20believes%20AI%20optimism%2C%20which%20has%20driven%20the%20lion's%20share%20of%20the%20rally%2C%20is%20already%20fully%20priced%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20high%20expectations%20are%20visible%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20Shiller%20cyclically%20adjusted%20price-to-earnings%20ratio%2C%20Arnott%20said%2C%20which%20sits%20at%20levels%20that%20rival%20the%20dot-com%20bubble%20peak.%20At%2037%20times%20earnings%2C%20just%20below%20the%20late-2021%20peak%20of%2038%2C%20before%20the%20market%20fell%20by%2025%25%2C%20and%20the%202000%20peak%20of%2043%2C%20right%20in%20front%20of%20a%2050%25%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221242%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22s%26amp%3Bp%20500%20cape%20ratio%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67379b5afa0140cdd563d0d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22943%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGuruFocus%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20with%20high%20expectations%20is%20that%20the%20results%20eventually%20have%20to%20live%20up%20to%20them.%20But%20a%20couple%20of%20factors%20threaten%20the%20market's%20bullish%20narrative%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20is%20that%20companies%20like%20Nvidia%20will%20be%20able%20to%20keep%20their%2090%25%20market%20share%20as%20competition%20rises%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20chips%20eventually%20comes%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20posed%20the%20question%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20presumption%20would%20have%20been%20that%20Intel%20would%20be%20the%20dominant%20player%2C%26quot%3B%20Arnott%20said.%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20Intel%20is%20teetering%20perilously%20close%20to%20irrelevance%2C%20and%20Nvidia%20wasn't%20on%20anyone's%20radar%20screen%20five%20years%20ago.%20So%20disruptors%20get%20disrupted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20the%20possibility%20that%20the%20pace%20of%20AI%20adoption%20is%20slower%20than%20expected%2C%20Arnott%20said.%20He%20said%20internet%20use%20in%202005%20wasn't%20all%20that%20different%20from%20its%20use%20in%202000%2C%20but%20that%20today%2C%20things%20have%20completely%20changed.%20A%20longer%20timeline%20may%20play%20out%20for%20AI%20as%20well%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArnott%20joins%20a%20long%20list%20of%20strategists%20and%20money%20managers%20who%20have%20recently%20expressed%20lackluster%20outlooks%20about%20forward%20return%20prospects%2C%20given%20the%20state%20of%20stock%20valuations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs'%20Chief%20US%20Equity%20Strategist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsp500-outlook-next-decade-forecast-david-kostin-goldman-stocks-strategist-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDavid%20Kostin%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20waves%20in%20October%20when%20he%20said%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20would%20deliver%203%25%20annualized%20returns%20over%20the%20next%2010%20years.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider%2C%20he%20also%20made%20a%20similar%20point%20to%20Arnott%20in%20that%20the%20valuations%20of%20some%20of%20the%20market's%20most-loved%20names%20are%20much%20higher%20than%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20pack%2C%20similar%20to%20what%20happened%20during%20the%20dot-com%20bubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22882%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Goldman%20Sachs%20chart%20showing%2010%20largest%20stocks%20trading%20at%2031x%20P%2FE%20compared%20to%2019x%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20market.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6729024f5ec9bfa3d63b8e71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22730%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America's%20Global%20Chief%20Equity%20Strategist%20Michael%20Hartnett%20said%20in%20a%20client%20note%20on%20Friday%20that%20US%20stocks%20have%20outperformed%20relative%20to%20equities%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20to%20the%20most%20extreme%20degree%20in%20at%20least%2075%20years.%20Relative%20performance%20levels%20have%20reached%20elevated%20levels%20in%20prior%20asset%20bubbles%20like%20the%20so-called%20Nifty%20Fifty%20and%20dot-com%20peaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221154%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22us%20stocks%20vs%20rest%20of%20the%20world%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67379c01ede4eeae3927ef48%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22669%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Hartnett%20said%20it's%20difficult%20to%20call%20the%20top%20in%20investor%20sentiment%2C%20the%20strategist%20known%20for%20his%20short-winded%20writing%20simply%20said%3A%20%26quot%3Bsell%20hubris%2C%20buy%20humiliation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20both%20Arnott%20and%20Hartnett%20say%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20call%20the%20top.%20As%20short-term%20interest%20rates%20fall%20and%20the%20market-friendly%20policies%20of%20the%20Trump%20administration%20on%20the%20way%2C%20the%20rally%20could%20continue%20for%20months%20or%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20history%20shows%20there%20will%20likely%20eventually%20be%20cheaper%20times%20to%20buy%20into%20the%20market%2C%20said%20David%20Einhorn%2C%20founder%20of%20hedge%20fund%20Greenlight%20Capital%2C%20at%20CNBC's%20Delivering%20Alpha%20conference%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20really%2C%20really%2C%20really%20pricey%20environment%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20necessarily%20make%20me%20bearish.%20Asset%20prices%20can%20trade%20at%20the%20wrong%20price%20and%20they%20can%20trade%20at%20the%20wrong%20price%20for%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Einhorn%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20observe%20that%20it's%20a%20really%20expensive%20market%20that%20if%20you%20buy%20and%20hold%20for%20a%20very%20long%20period%20of%20time%2C%20I%20doubt%20that%20this%20is%20a%20great%20%E2%80%94%20you'll%20look%20back%20and%20say%20this%20was%20a%20great%20entry%20point%20of%20all%20of%20the%20entry%20points%20that%20you%20could%20have.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20Arnott%20sees%20things%2C%20that%20better%20entry%20point%20could%20come%20in%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-rob-arnott-warns-bear-market-tech-bubble-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731751202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6658b8d11cd3b1779041aca3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-rob-arnott-warns-bear-market-tech-bubble-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAre%20we%20likely%20to%20see%20a%20bear%20market%20in%20the%20next%20two%20years%20for%20large-cap%20growth%3F%20Yeah.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Radu%20Jude%20Discusses%20How%20Andy%20Warhol%20Film%20Began%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98Joke%2C%E2%80%99%20Says%20Filmmakers%20Need%20to%20Be%20%E2%80%98Serious%20About%20TikTok%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731751021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%