20get%20answers%20when%20I%20felt%20off.%20At%2045%2C%20I've%20learned%20to%20listen%20to%20my%20body.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225973%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Young%20adult%20woman%20suffering%20from%20abdominal%20pains%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67350528fa0140cdd5632baa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20(not%20pictured)%20thought%20she%20was%20going%20through%20perimenopause.%3Cp%3EJulPo%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20menstrual%20bleeding%20was%20abnormal%2C%20so%20I%20went%20to%20my%20doctor%2C%20thinking%20I%20was%20in%20perimenopause.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20hormone%20tests%20said%20I%20was%20nowhere%20near%20that%20despite%20being%20in%20my%2040s.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAdvocating%20for%20myself%20led%20my%20doctors%20to%20find%20a%20uterine%20fibroid%20that%20was%20painful.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFour%20months%20ago%2C%20I%20went%20in%20to%20see%20my%20primary%20care%20doctor%20because%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Freproductive-health%2Fsigns-youre-losing-too-much-blood-during-period%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emenstrual%20bleeding%20was%20abnormal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20However%2C%20even%20in%20my%2040s%2C%20I%20wasn't%20exactly%20sure%20how%20to%20define%20%26quot%3Bnormal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20convinced%20I%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperimenopause-felt-like-going-through-puberty-again-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egoing%20through%20perimenopause%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20my%20hormonal%20levels%20said%20otherwise.%20I%20had%20to%20advocate%20for%20myself%20to%20get%20answers.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b14d246-4b08-463f-847c-196e26a08893%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20dealt%20with%20my%20period%20for%20what%20felt%20like%20forever%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20started%20with%20the%20secretive%20all-girls%20meeting%20about%20periods%20in%20the%20fifth%20grade.%20Of%20course%2C%20we%20couldn't%20let%20the%20boys%20know%20we%20were%20learning%20about%20menstruation.%20There%2C%20I%20learned%20the%20basics%20about%20cramps%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Freproductive-health%2Ftampons-vs-pads%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edifference%20between%20pads%20and%20tampons%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20the%20non-stop%20fun%20that%20awaited%20me%20with%20my%20changing%20body.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20my%20peer%20group%20reached%20our%20child-bearing%20years%2C%20the%20whispers%20turned%20to%20audible%20conversation.%20Some%20friends%20became%20pregnant%2C%20while%20others%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-wants-children-husband-suffers-from-male-infertility-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estruggled%20with%20infertility%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20We%20talked%20about%20IVF%20and%20birth%20plans.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%20we%20reached%20our%2040s%2C%20and%20in%20happy%20hours%20and%20Facebook%20groups%2C%20the%20voices%20turned%20to%20shouts%20about%20that%20ever-present%20p-word%3A%20Perimenopause.%20Any%20negative%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20night%20sweats%2C%20uncontrollable%20emotions%2C%20sleep%20challenges%20%E2%80%94%20was%20attributed%20to%20perimenopause%2C%20so%20when%20I%20started%20having%20irregular%20bleeding%2C%20I%20knew%20it%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperimenopause-is-giving-me-rage-as-a-symptom-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emust%20be%20perimenopause%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELike%20the%20pesky%20gray%20hairs%20I%20pluck%20(against%20the%20wishes%20of%20my%20hairstylist)%20and%20my%2011%20lines%20that%20feel%20like%20old%20friends%2C%20I%20resignedly%20accepted%20this%20as%20an%20unwelcome%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsimple-tests-show-how-well-aging-do-now-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esign%20of%20aging%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20started%20to%20pray%20for%20menopause%20so%20the%20bleeding%20and%20sometimes%20debilitating%20cramping%20would%20stop.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e1f73985-e91b-41c4-b6c5-afd8084496f3%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20decided%20to%20listen%20to%20my%20body%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESubsequent%20yearly%20doctor's%20appointments%20led%20to%20a%20diagnosed%20cyst%2C%20and%20eventual%20blood%20tests%20that%20determined%20my%20hormone%20levels%20didn't%20indicate%20the%20start%20of%20menopause.%20I%20carried%20on%20with%20my%20annoyingly%20random%20mid-cycle%20bleeding.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFinally%2C%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202024%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20listen%20to%20my%20body.%20I'd%20been%20having%20my%20period%20for%20decades%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20this%20wasn't%20%26quot%3Bnormal%26quot%3B%20bleeding.%20Maybe%20it%20was%20perimenopause%2C%20but%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20push%20for%20some%20answers.%20On%20a%20particularly%20terrible%20morning%2C%20I%20called%20the%20nurse%20line%20at%20my%20local%20clinic%2C%20answered%20a%20lengthy%20list%20of%20personal%20questions%2C%20and%20was%20scheduled%20to%20see%20my%20primary%20care%20provider.%20More%20bloodwork%20and%20a%20pap%20smear%20later%2C%20my%20doctor%20ordered%20an%20ultrasound.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20then%20we%20had%20an%20answer%20(two%20of%20them%2C%20actually)%3A%20a%20uterine%20fibroid%20and%20an%20endometrial%20polyp.%20Reading%20a%20list%20of%20symptoms%20%E2%80%94%20bleeding%20between%20periods%2C%20pelvic%20pain%2C%20longer%20periods%20%E2%80%94%20felt%20like%20reading%20a%20page%20of%20my%20journal%20for%20the%20last%20few%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI've%20since%20learned%20that%20many%20women%20deal%20with%20fibroids%20throughout%20their%20lives%20%E2%80%94%20up%20to%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hopkinsmedicine.org%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-and-diseases%2Futerine-fibroids%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAn%2520estimated%252020%2525%2520to%252050%2Cso%2520they%2520are%2520often%2520undiagnosed.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%2077%25%20of%20women%20in%20their%20childbearing%20years%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%94%20many%20of%20whom%20I%20knew%20in%20my%20real%20life.%20We%20were%20just%20too%20busy%20talking%20about%20perimenopause%20to%20discuss%20these%20other%20issues.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20followed%20up%20with%20a%20specialist%20who%20talked%20through%20my%20options%2C%20and%20after%20years%20of%20suffering%2C%20I%20was%20ready%20for%20a%20solution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20same%20day%20as%20my%2045th%20birthday%2C%20I%20had%20a%20dilation%20and%20curettage%20procedure%20to%20biopsy%20my%20endometrium%20and%20remove%20the%20polyp.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20a%20woman%20who%20has%20never%20been%20pregnant%20or%20birthed%20a%20baby%2C%20walking%20into%20the%20procedure%20room%20was%20jarring.%20However%2C%20the%20medical%20assistant%20and%20doctor%20were%20reassuring%20and%20calming%20throughout%20the%20process.%20I%20practiced%20some%20deep%20breathing%20during%20the%20painful%20parts%20and%20said%20a%20short%20prayer%20that%20the%20biopsy%20was%20benign.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%20that%20night%2C%20I%20celebrated%20my%20birthday%20with%20a%20family%20dinner%2C%20and%20my%20birthday%20celebration%20stretched%20into%20a%20week%20lat