that%20the%20keys%20to%20defeating%20Russia's%20invasion%20now%20can%20be%20found%20in%20the%20Soviet%20Union's%20multi-pronged%20strategy%20in%20Vietnam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20Marines%20wade%20through%20a%20rice%20paddy%20in%20an%20assault%20on%20Viet%20Cong%20positions%20in%201965.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67367530ede4eeae3927ba84%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221383%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECrucial%20ways%20to%20defeat%20Russia's%20invasion%20can%20be%20found%20in%20the%20Soviet%20Union's%20multi-pronged%20strategy%20in%20Vietnam%2C%20analyst%20Oleksandr%20Danylyuk%20says.%20Here%2C%20US%20Marines%20wade%20through%20a%20rice%20paddy%20in%20an%20assault%20on%20Viet%20Cong%20positions%20in%201965.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FJohn%20T.%20Wheeler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20prong%20of%20this%20strategy%20would%20be%20to%20%26quot%3Bstabilize%20the%20frontline%20and%20to%20render%20any%20successful%20offensive%20actions%20by%20Russian%20troops%20impossible.%26quot%3B%20This%20would%20require%20stopping%20the%20Russian%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-turns-tables-russia-drops-glide-bombs-on-its-territory-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eglide%20bomb%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20attacks%20that%20are%20devastating%20Ukrainian%20frontline%20positions.%20Rather%20than%20trying%20to%20stop%20the%20bombs%20themselves%2C%20Danylyuk%20suggests%20the%20West%20provide%20more%20fighters%20armed%20with%20long-range%20air-to-air%20missiles%20%E2%80%94%20in%20particular%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-ukraine-needs-gripen-fighter-jets-long-term-f-16s-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESweden's%20Gripen%20jet%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20Meteor%20missiles%20%E2%80%94%20to