0cover%20care%20for%20individuals%20with%20preexisting%20conditions%2C%20like%20asthma%2C%20heart%20disease%2C%20and%20diabetes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYunan%20Ji%20is%20an%20assistant%20professor%20and%20economist%20at%20Georgetown%20University%20with%20an%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eexpertise%20in%20healthcare%20policy.%20She%20told%20BI%20that%20reducing%20or%20repealing%20ACA%20coverage%20%E2%80%94%20which%20Trump%20proposed%20during%20his%20first-term%20%E2%80%94%20could%20be%20detrimental%20to%20Americans%20with%20preexisting%20conditions%2C%20who%20may%20lose%20their%20coverage%20or%20have%20to%20pay%20more%20for%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20purchase%20insurance%20to%20protect%20against%20future%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20Ji%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20make%20people%20go%20into%20a%20different%20risk%20pool%20when%20they%20require%20care%20for%20some%20medical%20condition%2C%20that%20defeats%20the%20purpose%20of%20insurance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20also%20voiced%20support%20for%20privatizing%20more%20of%20the%20healthcare%20sector.%20This%20could%20mean%20some%20Americans%20on%20ACA%20plans%20could%20face%20higher%20out-of-pocket%20costs%20and%20fewer%20in-network%20care%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-passes-inflation-reduction-act-sending-it-to-biden-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInflation%20Reduction%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20took%20steps%20to%20lower%20the%20cost%20of%20prescription%20drugs%20and%20cap%20out-of-pocket%20costs%20for%20Medicare%20beneficiaries.%20The%20legislation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2024%2F02%2F07%2Ftrump-medicare-price-negotiations-executive-power%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erequires%3C%2Fa%3E%20Trump%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20continue%20existing%20drug%20price%20negotiations%20through%20at%20least%20the%20end%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221380ef