%20built%20a%2020-inch%20neck%20with%20neck%20bridges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731742026000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115355407%2Cimgsize-37620.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fboxing%2Fhow-an-18-year-old-mike-tyson-built-a-20-inch-neck-with-neck-bridges-watch%2Farticleshow%2F115355364.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mike%20Tyson%2C%20renowned%20for%20his%20incredible%20strength%20and%20boxing%20prowess%2C%20incorporated%20a%20unique%20exercise%20called%20neck%20bridges%20into%20his%20rigorous%20training%20routine.%20This%20technique%2C%20aimed%20at%20strengthening%20neck%20muscles%2C%20involved%20supporting%20his%20body%20weight%20solely%20with%20his%20head%20and%20feet.%20However%2C%20in%20a%20recent%20match%2C%20Tyson%20was%20defeated%20by%20Jake%20Paul%2C%20a%20younger%20social%20media%20personality%20turned%20boxer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fboxing%2Fhow-an-18-year-old-mike-tyson-built-a-20-inch-neck-with-neck-bridges-watch%2Farticleshow%2F115355364.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2210%20Newborns%20Killed%20In%20UP%20Hospital%20Fire%2C%20Parents%20Protest%20To%20Meet%20Survivors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2016%20children%20are%20battling%20for%20their%20lives%20while%2010%20newborns%20died%20as%20a%20fire%20broke%20out%20last%20night%20at%20a%20hospital%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Jhansi.%20The%20fire%20erupted%20in%20the%20Maharani%20Laxmi%20Bai%20Medical%20College's%20neonatal%20intensive%20care%20unit%20(NICU)%20around%2010%3A45%20pm%2C%20said%20District%20Magistrate%20(DM)%20Avinash%20Kumar%2C%20who%20confirmed%20the%20casualties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2054%20children%20were%20admitted%20to%20the%20NICU%20at%20that%20moment%20as%20officials%20swung%20into%20action%20and%20rescued%2044%20newborns.%20Seven%20of%20the%2010%20victims%20have%20been%20identified%2C%20said%20an%20official%2C%20adding%20that%20DNA%20tests%20will%20be%20carried%20out%20if%20needed%20to%20identify%20the%20rest%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaos%20erupted%20at%20the%20hospital%20again%20this%20morning%20after%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20injured%20children%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20meet%20them.%20The%20angry%20relatives%20are%20now%20camping%20at%20the%20hospital%20in%20protest%20after%20they%20were%20stopped%20from%20staging%20a%20road%20blockade.%20Sources%20suggest%20the%20parents%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20meet%20their%20children%20injured%20in%20the%20fire%20to%20avoid%20any%20confusion%20over%20the%20identities%20of%20the%20infants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShort-circuit%20caused%20fire%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20short-circuit%20inside%20the%20oxygen%20concentrator%20possibly%20caused%20the%20fire%2C%20said%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Brajesh%20Pathak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20showed%20panic-struck%20patients%20and%20their%20caretakers%20outside%20the%20hospital%20and%20several%20charred%20medical%20equipment%20inside.%20A%20woman%20who%20lost%20her%20child%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%20she%20couldn't%20find%20her%20baby%20after%20the%20incident%20and%20was%20informed%20later%20the%20baby%20had%20died.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(SSP)%20Jhansi%20Sudha%20Singh%20said%20early%20this%20morning%20that%2016%20children%20who%20suffered%20injuries%20are%20being%20treated%20at%20local%20hospitals%20and%20that%20efforts%20are%20on%20to%20save%20them.%20All%20doctors%20are%20available%20for%20them%2C%20along%20with%20adequate%20medical%20facilities%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UP%20government%20has%20also%20denied%20charges%20that%20fire%20alarms%20and%20other%20safety%20systems%20at%20the%20hospital%20were%20not%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pathak%2C%20who%20also%20holds%20the%20health%20portfolio%2C%20said%20the%20fire%20safety%20audit%20of%20the%20hospital%20was%20carried%20out%20in%20February%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20mock%20fire%20drill%20in%20June.%20%26quot%3BOn%20how%20and%20why%20it%20happened%2C%20we%20can%20say%20something%20about%20it%20once%20the%20probe%20report%20comes%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Pathak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20there%20will%20be%20three%20levels%20of%20investigation%20into%20the%20fire%20-%20one%20each%20by%20the%20health%20department%2C%20the%20police%2C%20and%20a%20magisterial%20inquiry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EGovernment's%20assistance%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20last%20night%20ordered%20senior%20officials%20and%20doctors%20to%20conduct%20rescue%20operations%20on%20a%20war%20footing%20and%20asked%20for%20the%20deployment%20of%20adequate%20fire-fighting%20vehicles.%20He%20has%20announced%20Rs%205%20lakh%20financial%20assistance%20for%20the%20families%20of%20the%20victims.%20Those%20who%20suffered%20serious%20injuries%20will%20get%20Rs%2050%2C000%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20also%20directed%20the%20Divisional%20Commissioner%20and%20the%20Deputy%20Inspector%20General%20(DIG)%20of%20Jhansi%20to%20submit%20a%20report%20within%2012%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20too%20have%20expressed%20grief%20over%20the%20fire%20tragedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20news%20of%20the%20death%20of%20several%20newborn%20babies%20in%20the%20accident%20at%20Maharani%20Laxmi%20Bai%20Medical%20College%2C%20Jhansi%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20is%20extremely%20heartbreaking.%20May%20God%20give%20strength%20to%20the%20bereaved%20parents%20and%20families%20to%20bear%20this%20cruel%20blow.%20I%20pray%20for%20the%20speedy%20recovery%20of%20the%20injured%20babies%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20President%20Murmu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20fire%20incident%20%26quot%3Bheartbreaking%26quot%3B%2C%C2%A0PM%20Modi%20has%20announced%20Rs%202%20lakh%20from%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20National%20Relief%20Fund%20for%20the%20victims'%20families%20and%20Rs%2050%2C000%20for%20the%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20those%20who%20have%20lost%20their%20innocent%20children%20in%20this.%20I%20pray%20to%20God%20to%20give%20them%20the%20strength%20to%20bear%20this%20immense%20loss.%20The%20local%20administration%2C%20under%20the%20supervision%20of%20the%20state%20government%2C%20is%20making%20every%20possible%20effort%20for%20relief%20and%20rescue%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20has%20alleged%20negligence%20by%20the%20hospital%20administration%20with%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20demanding%20action%20against%20those%20responsible.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731742020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F2cvae97_jhansi-hospital-fire_625x300_16_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjhansi-hospital-fire-10-newborns-killed-in-up-hospital-fire-efforts-on-to-save-16-others-7030974%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%2016%20children%20are%20battling%20for%20their%20lives%20while%2010%20newborns%20died%20as%20a%20fire%20broke%20out%20last%20night%20at%20a%20hospital%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Jhansi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22For%20Kolkata's%20Iconic%20Howrah%20Bridge%2C%20First%20'Health'%20Break%20In%20Over%203%20Decades%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%2081-year-old%20iconic%20Howrah%20Bridge%20(Rabindra%20Setu)%20--%20that%20connects%20the%20cities%20of%20Kolkata%20and%20Howrah%20--%20will%20remain%20closed%20to%20traffic%20for%20five%20hours%20on%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20Saturday%20and%20Sunday%20for%20a%20comprehensive%20health%20check-up%2C%20the%20Syama%20Prasad%20Mookerjee%20Port%20(SMP)%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20has%20notified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESMP%2C%20Kolkata%20is%20the%20custodian%20of%20the%20bridge%20and%20is%20responsible%20for%20its%20maintenance%20and%20upgrades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20health%20check-up%20of%20the%20bridge%20was%20conducted%20between%201983%20and%201988%2C%20after%20it%20remained%20in%20operation%20for%2040%20years%2C%20an%20SMP%2C%20Kolkata%20official%20said.%20The%20latest%20health%20check-up%20will%20be%20conducted%20by%20RITES%20Ltd%2C%20a%20public%20sector%20undertaking%20that%20is%20tasked%20with%20the%20maintenance%20of%20the%20Howrah%20Bridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bridge%2C%20a%20suspension-type%20balanced%20cantilever%20structure%2C%20is%20the%20sixth%20longest%20of%20its%20kind%20in%20the%20world.%20Despite%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Vidyasagar%20Setu%20across%20Hooghly%2C%20the%20Howrah%20Bridge%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20busiest%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20estimated%20100%2C000%20vehicles%20and%201%2C50%2C000%20pedestrians%20cross%20the%20bridge%20daily.%20What%20makes%20the%20bridge%20so%20alluring%20is%20its%20proximity%20to%20the%20Howrah%20railway%20station%20--%20one%20of%20the%20busiest%20in%20the%20world%20--%20which%20is%20still%20considered%20a%20gateway%20to%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20comprehensive%20health%20check-up%20of%20the%20bridge%20is%20important%20as%20it%20handles%20so%20much%20traffic.%20It%20is%20an%20iconic%20structure%20that%20has%20captured%20the%20imagination%20of%20artists%2C%20filmmakers%20and%20the%20common%20man.%20No%20illustration%20of%20Kolkata%20is%20complete%20without%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Howrah%20Bridge%20peeping%20out%20from%20somewhere%20in%20the%20frame.%20The%20bridge%20was%20commissioned%20in%201943%20during%20World%20War%20II%2C%20even%20as%20the%20Japanese%20were%20bombing%20Kolkata%20(then%20Calcutta).%20To%20keep%20the%20bridge%20safe%20from%20Japanese%20bombers%2C%20the%20commissioning%20was%20done%20at%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bridge%20also%20brought%20into%20focus%20the%20capability%20of%20Indian%20industry%20to%20produce%20high-quality%20tensile%20steel%2C%20even%20under%20British%20rule.%20Construction%20of%20the%20bridge%20started%20with%20steel%20sent%20from%20England.%20This%20supply%20had%20to%20be%20stopped%20though%20as%20steel%20produced%20in%20England%20was%20required%20for%20the%20war%20effort.%20It%20was%20Tata%20Steel%20that%20came%20up%20with%20tensile%20steel%20of%20the%20quality%20required%20for%20the%20Bridge%20and%20the%20rest%20is%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHence%2C%20we%20are%20really%20proud%20of%20this%20Bridge%20that%20was%20built%20with%20high-quality%20steel%20produced%20by%20an%20Indian%20manufacturer%2C%20even%20when%20the%20country%20was%20under%20colonial%20rule.%20We%20would%20like%20Howrah%20Bridge%20to%20remain%20in%20service%20for%20several%20more%20decades%2C%20hence%20the%20health%20check-up%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731741360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-01%2Fkolkata-howrah-bridge-istock-photo_650x400_61451884593.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkolkata-news%2Fkolkatas-iconic-howrah-bridge-to-shut-for-5-hours-for-health-checkup-7028166%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2081-year-old%20iconic%20Howrah%20Bridge%20(Rabindra%20Setu)%20--%20that%20connects%20the%20cities%20of%20Kolkata%20and%20Howrah%20--%20will%20remain%20closed%20to%20traffic%20for%20five%20hours%20on%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20Saturday%20and%20Sunday%20for%20a%20comprehensive%20health%20check-up.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%2