0blanketed%20the%20city%2C%20with%20the%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%20recorded%20at%20406%20this%20morning%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(CPCB).%20The%20smog%20and%20pollution%20are%20causing%20severe%20health%20concerns%2C%20including%20respiratory%20distress%2C%20eye%20irritation%2C%20and%20heightened%20risks%20of%20cardiovascular%20complications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrone%20footage%20from%20Saturday%20morning%20at%20key%20locations%20such%20as%20AIIMS%20and%20Pragati%20Maidan%20shows%20a%20layer%20of%20smog%20still%20lingering%20in%20the%20air.%20At%20Pragati%20Maidan%2C%20the%20AQI%20stood%20at%20357%2C%20a%20level%20classified%20as%20'very%20poor.'%20Other%20hotspots%2C%20including%20Kalindi%20Kunj%20and%20India%20Gate%2C%20reported%20AQI%20levels%20of%20414%20and%20above%2C%20putting%20them%20in%20the%20'severe'%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20high-rise%20buildings%20in%20areas%20like%20Kalindi%20Kunj%20appeared%20shrouded%20in%20a%20gray%20haze%2C%20while%20parts%20of%20the%20Yamuna%20river%20near%20Okhla%20Barrage%20were%20covered%20with%20toxic%20foam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Delhi%20continues%20to%20be%20covered%20in%20a%20blanket%20of%20smog%20in%20the%20mornings%20as%20the%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%20continues%20to%20be%20in%20'Severe'%20category%20in%20several%20areas%20as%20per%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(CPCB)%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn(Drone%20visuals%20from%20Signature%20Bridge%20shot%20at%208%3A45%20am)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fq6uMZdQHhU%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fq6uMZdQHhU%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1857631511429918876%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2016%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20toxic%20smog%20blankets%20India's%20capital%2C%20the%20Delhi%20government%20has%20implemented%20stringent%20measures%20to%20curb%20pollution%20under%20Stage%20III%20of%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20banned%20the%20operation%20of%20BS-III%20petrol%20and%20BS-IV%20diesel%20four-wheelers%20across%20the%20national%20capital.%20Violators%20will%20face%20penalties%20under%20Section%20194(1)%20of%20the%20Motor%20Vehicle%20Act%2C%201988%2C%20which%20translates%20to%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%2020%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20vehicle-related%20restrictions%20include%20prohibition%20of%20diesel-operated%20Medium%20Goods%20Vehicles%20(MGVs)%20of%20BS-III%20standards%20or%20below%20within%20Delhi%2C%20unless%20transporting%20essential%20goods%20or%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERestrictions%20have%20been%20implemented%20for%20diesel%20Light%20Commercial%20Vehicles%20(LCVs)%20registered%20outside%20Delhi%2C%20with%20exceptions%20for%20essential%20services.%20A%20ban%20has%20been%20imposed%20on%20interstate%20buses%2C%20except%20for%20those%20powered%20by%20electric%2C%20CNG%2C%20or%20BS-VI%20diesel%20engines%2C%20unless%20operating%20under%20an%20All%20India%20Tourist%20Permit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGraded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP-III)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGRAP-III%2C%20enacted%20by%20the%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%20(CAQM)%2C%20brings%20a%20suite%20of%20interventions%20to%20combat%20severe%20pollution.%20These%20include%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntensified%20road%20sweeping%20and%20water%20sprinkling%2C%20especially%20on%20heavy%20traffic%20corridors%20and%20pollution%20hotspots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20complete%20ban%20on%20demolition%2C%20earth%20excavation%2C%20and%20transportation%20of%20construction%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnhanced%20public%20transport%20services%2C%20including%20the%20deployment%20of%20106%20additional%20shuttle%20buses%20and%20increased%20metro%20train%20trips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EStaggered%20Office%20Timings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%20announced%20yesterday%20staggered%20timings%20for%20government%20offices%20in%20the%20city%20to%20ease%20traffic%20congestion%20given%20the%20pollution%20levels.%20Under%20the%20schedule%2C%20central%20government%20offices%20will%20operate%20from%209%20am%20to%205%3A30%20pm%2C%20Delhi%20government%20offices%20from%2010%20am%20to%206%3A30%20pm%2C%20and%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20(MCD)%20offices%20from%208%3A30%20am%20to%205%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20LG%20VK%20Saxena%20issued%20a%20note%20approving%20the%20staggered%20government%20office%20timings%20till%20February%202025%2C%20expressing%20dissatisfaction%20that%20a%20measure%20that%20should%20have%20been%20in%20place%20as%20a%20pre-emptive%20step%20was%20implemented%20with%20a%20delay%20of%20several%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESchools%20for%20children%20up%20to%20Class%205%20will%20transition%20to%20online%20learning%20after%20the%20weekend.%20%C2%A0Private%20construction%20and%20demolition%20activities%20are%20suspended%2C%20while%20government%20projects%20deemed%20essential%20will%20continue.%20Transport%20department%20teams%2C%20with%20280%20personnel%2C%20have%20been%20deployed%20to%20enforce%20these%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731729900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fakeufi0o_delhi-pollution-ani-_625x300_16_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-delhi-pollution-curbs-ban-on-these-vehicles-staggered-office-timings-7031055%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Air%20Pollution%3A%20Delhi%20continued%20to%20battle%20a%20worsening%20pollution%20crisis%2C%20with%20its%20air%20quality%20plungi