%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-hints-big-change-to-openai-investments-sec-filing-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20product%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Copilot%2C%20with%20sweeping%20fanfare.%20%26quot%3BCopilot%20will%20fundamentally%20transform%20our%20relationship%20with%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20declared.%20The%20AI%20assistant%2C%20he%20predicted%2C%20would%20give%20birth%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Bera%20that%20uplifts%20every%20person%2C%20industry%2C%20community%2C%20and%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20a%20year%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-mustafa-suleyman-ai-copilot-update-reviews-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECopilot's%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20reviews%20%E2%80%94%20both%20inside%20and%20outside%20Microsoft%20%E2%80%94%20indicate%20that%20the%20new%20product%20is%20struggling%20to%20live%20up%20to%20the%20hype.%20While%20there%20is%20no%20single%20measurement%20of%20Copilot's%20performance%2C%20given%20the%20wide%20array%20of%20features%20it%20seeks%20to%20provide%2C%20many%20customers%20appear%20to%20be%20dissatisfied%20with%20the%20AI%20tool%2C%20complaining%20that%20it%20is%20ineffective%2C%20costly%2C%20and%20not%20secure.%20In%20October%2C%20when%20the%20management%20consultancy%20Gartner%20published%20a%20survey%20of%20123%20IT%20leaders%2C%20only%20four%20said%20Copilot%20provided%20significant%20value%20to%20their%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20Microsoft's%20own%20employees%20and%20executives%20are%20privately%20concerned%20that%20Copilot%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20deliver%20on%20its%20ambitions.%20To%20assess%20the%20tool's%20rollout%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20central%20role%20it%20plays%20in%20Microsoft's%20historic%2C%20all-out%20investment%20in%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20Business%20Insider%20reviewed%20internal%20emails%20and%20pay%20spreadsheets%2C%20spoke%20with%20customers%20and%20competitors%2C%20and%20interviewed%2015%20current%20and%20former