lete%20at%20their%20convenience%20to%20enhance%20their%20technical%20skills.%20This%20platform%20is%20available%20to%20all%20students%20who%20register.%20The%20courses%20cover%20a%20range%20of%20topics%20%E2%80%94%20from%20building%20apps%20using%20Flutter%20to%20creating%20websites%2C%20web%20development%20skills%2C%20and%20working%20with%20Raspberry%20Pi%203%20%E2%80%94%20providing%20a%20high%20level%20of%20technical%20understanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2030%2C000%20course%20completion%20certificates%20have%20been%20issued%2C%20and%20over%2016%2C000%20unique%20students%20have%20received%20course%20completion%20certificates%20as%20of%20March%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20providing%20a%20platform%20that%20transcends%20entrepreneurial%20incubation%2C%20thingQbator%20is%20empowering%20young%20Indians%20to%20become%20the%20driving%20force%20behind%20technology%20and%20innovation.%20This%20initiative%20serves%20as%20a%20powerful%20catalyst%2C%20propelling%20the%20vision%20of%20a%20technologically%20advanced%20and%20socially%20empowered%20India%20into%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20truly%20believe%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20ignite%20the%20imaginations%20of%20young%20minds%2C%20and%20universities%20and%20other%20educational%20institutions%20are%20the%20ideal%20environments%20to%20encourage%20them%20to%20explore%20new%20ideas.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20we%20aim%20to%20do%20through%20our%20thingQbator%20programme%20%E2%80%93%20we%20collaborate%20with%20universities%20to%20identify%20and%20mentor%20young%20minds%2C%20helping%20them%20shape%20and%20realize%20their%20entrepreneurial%20aspirations.%20This%20initiative%20is%20not%20just%20about%20nurturing%20startups%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20empowering%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20innovators%20to%20create%20impactful%20solutions%20for%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Harish%20Krishnan%2C%20Managing%20Director%20%26amp%3B%20Chief%20Policy%20Officer%2C%20Cisco%20India%20%26amp%3B%20SAARC.%3C%2F