resentatives%20%E2%80%94%20who%20were%20present%20at%20the%20previous%20year%E2%80%99s%20showing%20%E2%80%94%20opened%20their%20hearts%20and%20the%20entire%20campus%20to%20provide%20space%20to%20these%20artists.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20time%2C%20we%20organised%20the%20residency%20on%20their%20campus%2C%20where%20students%20practised%20in%20the%20central%20garden%2C%20right%20in%20front%20of%20the%20hospital.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20even%20patients%20could%20enjoy%20the%20music%2C%20creating%20a%20unique%20atmosphere%20of%20healing%20and%20cultural%20exchange%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhati%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20shares%20touching%20stories%2C%20like%20one%20where%20a%20son%2C%20while%20waiting%20for%20his%20father%20who%20was%20undergoing%20chemotherapy%2C%20sat%20and%20watched%20the%20students%20play%2C%20enjoying%20the%20music.%20It%E2%80%99s%20moments%20like%20these%20that%2C%20without%20a%20doubt%2C%20help%20people%20navigate%20the%20challenges%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%204569px)%20100vw%2C%204569px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-DEV09823_11zon-1731069265.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%224569%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Young%20women%20from%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20folk%20music%20communities%20performing%20together%20at%20the%20Lok%20Sangeet%20Shala%20residency%2C%20showcasing%20their%20talent%20and%20confidence%20in%20a%20supportive%20and%20trusting%20environment.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-DEV09823_11zon-1731069265.jpg%204569w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-DEV09823_11zon-1731069265-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-DEV09823_11zon-1731069265-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F202