trategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEssential%20advice%20for%20JEE%20aspirants%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20practical%20and%20insightful%20tips%20from%20Kalpit%20Veerwal%20that%20he%20believes%20are%20essential%20for%20cracking%20the%20JEE%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Build%20consistency%20in%20study%20routine%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20piece%20of%20advice%20I%E2%80%99d%20give%20is%20to%20be%20consistent%20in%20your%20studies%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kalpit%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20He%20stresses%20that%20consistent%20study%20is%20more%20effective%20than%20short%2C%20intense%20bursts%20of%20effort.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20students%20who%20study%20regularly%2C%20even%20for%20three%20to%20four%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20tend%20to%20outperform%20those%20who%20alternate%20between%20intense%20study%20sessions%20and%20periods%20of%20inactivity.%20The%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20sticking%20to%20a%20daily%20routine%20to%20steadily%20build%20your%20knowledge%20over%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Focus%20on%20problem-solving%20over%20theory%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKalpit%20advises%2C%20%E2%80%9CReading%20theory%20is%20important%2C%20but%20practice%20makes%20perfect.%20The%20exam%20is%20all%20about%20solving%20problems.%E2%80%9D%20Since%20the%20JEE%20is%20a%20test%20of%20application%20rather%20than%20knowledge%2C%20he%20recommends%20solving%20as%20many%20problems%20as%20possible%20to%20deeply%20understand%20the%20concepts%20and%20sharpen%20your%20ability%20to%20tackle%20a%20variety%20of%20questions%20under%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Revise%20frequently%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20chapter%20must%20be%20revised%20at%20least%20five%20to%20s